snippet.title: Road Trip Europe
snippet.description:
Road Trip: Europe A Classic Hidden Object Game invites you on the trip of a lifetime. Explore beautiful locations spanning the entirety of Europe as you hunt for hidden objects. Hidden Object enthusiasts will rejoice with over 1,700 objects to locate across multiple game modes. Take a proper European holiday as you explore the open road and discover the sights that await.
Experience beautiful high resolution hidden object scenes. This is one road trip you won't want to miss.

• Enjoy hours of fun and relaxing gameplay.
• Solve bonus puzzles and minigames.
• Take on challenging gameplay, never frustrating!
